This paper proposes a novel cost-sensitive label embedding algorithm for multi-label classification. The algorithm is designed to optimize performance with respect to different cost functions, which is a common concern in machine learning applications. The paper discusses theoretical justifications for the algorithm and presents extensive experimental results to demonstrate its effectiveness. Given the focus on machine learning and classification, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
